Shao Cang was born with great talent.

123
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:02,270
Brimming with ambition, he was harmed by others.

124
00:07:02,510 --> 00:07:05,070
One day, we'll be buried under the same spring.

125
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,840
Let us have fun together in the next life.

126
00:07:08,670 --> 00:07:09,710
I'm a genius.

127
00:07:10,350 --> 00:07:11,010
Young Lord.

128
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:11,710
