198
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:03,990
You are...

199
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,770
Ji Yang.

200
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:13,110
Yes.

201
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:14,740
